{
  "info": {
    "name": "RutaExpress MVP — E1-E8",
    "description": "Variables de coleccion:\n\n**Azure (fase 1)**\n- `apim_base_url`: `terraform output -raw apim_gateway_url` (en mvp\\)\n- `apim_subscription_key`: APIM -> Subscriptions -> Built-in all-access (README 6.7)\n\n**AWS (fase 2)**\n- `aws_alb_base_url`: `http://` + `terraform output -raw aws_mobile_alb_dns`\n\n**E5** no tiene HTTP: ver carpeta E5 (portal Azure Service Bus q-dlq).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "apim_base_url",
      "value": "https://apim-rutaexpress-mvp.azure-api.net"
    },
    {
      "key": "apim_subscription_key",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "aws_alb_base_url",
      "value": "http://rutaexpress-mvp-mobile-alb-208219070.us-east-1.elb.amazonaws.com"
    },
    {
      "key": "idempotency_key",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Azure APIM (fase 1)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "E1 — Crear orden",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const key = pm.variables.replaceIn('{{$guid}}');",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('idempotency_key', key);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Idempotency-Key", "value": "{{idempotency_key}}" },
              { "key": "Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key", "value": "{{apim_subscription_key}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"customerId\": \"B2B-001\",\n  \"items\": [{ \"sku\": \"SKU-001\", \"quantity\": 1 }]\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{apim_base_url}}/api/v1/orders"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "E2 — Reintento misma Idempotency-Key",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Idempotency-Key", "value": "{{idempotency_key}}" },
              { "key": "Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key", "value": "{{apim_subscription_key}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"customerId\": \"B2B-001\",\n  \"items\": [{ \"sku\": \"SKU-001\", \"quantity\": 1 }]\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{apim_base_url}}/api/v1/orders"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "E3 — Sin stock (409)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('idempotency_key', pm.variables.replaceIn('{{$guid}}'));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Idempotency-Key", "value": "{{idempotency_key}}" },
              { "key": "Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key", "value": "{{apim_subscription_key}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"customerId\": \"B2B-002\",\n  \"items\": [{ \"sku\": \"SKU-001\", \"quantity\": 9999 }]\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{apim_base_url}}/api/v1/orders"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "E4 — WMS degradado (503)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('idempotency_key', pm.variables.replaceIn('{{$guid}}'));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Idempotency-Key", "value": "{{idempotency_key}}" },
              { "key": "X-Mock-Wms-Status", "value": "503" },
              { "key": "Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key", "value": "{{apim_subscription_key}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"customerId\": \"B2B-E4\",\n  \"items\": [{ \"sku\": \"SKU-001\", \"quantity\": 1 }]\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{apim_base_url}}/api/v1/orders"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "E8 — Tracking portal (stub)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key", "value": "{{apim_subscription_key}}" }
            ],
            "url": "{{apim_base_url}}/mock/portal/v1/tracking/ORD-123"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "E5 — DLQ replay (solo portal Azure)",
      "description": "No hay request HTTP en el MVP.\n\n1. Portal Azure -> Service Bus -> `sb-rutaexpress-mvp`\n2. Colas -> `q-dlq`\n3. Revisar mensajes fallidos y opcion de reenvio manual\n\nVer README 6.7 E5."
    },
    {
      "name": "AWS ALB (fase 2)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health — mobile-api",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{aws_alb_base_url}}/health"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "E6 — Completar entrega",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{}"
            },
            "url": "{{aws_alb_base_url}}/deliveries/123/complete"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "E7 — Evidencia hash valido (200)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"sha256\": \"a1b2c3d4e5f6789012345678901234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{aws_alb_base_url}}/deliveries/123/evidence"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "E7 — Evidencia hash invalido (400)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"sha256\": \"invalid\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{aws_alb_base_url}}/deliveries/123/evidence"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
